beer.beer_description:
For this birthday TIPA we pushed our house hazy yeast from Mogwai to the limit and built on what you loved about our recent dipa, foil hat society.

we hit it with a massive dry hop of strata (t90 & cgx), peacharine, and nelson, creating a ripe, complex character of stone fruit, citrus, and floral notes. the result is a thick, hazy beer with a lush mouthfeel that’s everything you want in a triple ipa

items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

You don't always intend to go for beers with a double digit ABV, but when you do, you make it count! Cheers to you, but be careful, 10% and up can really pack a punch. That's 45 different beers with an ABV of 10% and up. Try 5 more for Level 10!

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 305 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 62!
